summary:
Strategic communications manager with an external affairs background. My core strengths lie in building and executing a strong voice and branding for organizations. 

As the head of Marketing & Communications of Land Life Company I am responsible for the persona and story of a company that uses innovative technology solutions to be a force of good. Land Life Company plants trees, grows forests and restores nature. It is my job to share this impact with all stakeholders globally.  

Before joining Land Life, I worked as a freelancer for innovative scale ups,startups and agencies. I started my career as a Management Trainee at TNT. I hold a Master's degrees in International Relations from Utrecht University and a Master of honours in European Policy from the University of Amsterdam.
